\"><!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"wp-block-heading\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong><a href=\"/renaissance\">Эпоха Возрождения</a></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-medium-font-size\"><em><em><em><em>Эпоха Возрождения (XIV–XVI века) — это период невероятного расцвета искусства, науки и культуры в Европе. Этот период, начавшийся в Италии и распространившийся по всему континенту, стал мостом между Средневековьем и Новым временем. Возрождение подарило миру великих художников, учёных и мыслителей, чьи идеи и произведения до сих пор вдохновляют человечество.</em></em></em></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://project/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/8ce3a9b750dedc374e04be2813f48d05-677x1024.jpg\",\"id\":31,\"dimRatio\":50,\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover aligncenter\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"></span><img class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-31\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://project/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/8ce3a9b750dedc374e04be2813f48d05-677x1024.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\"/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">Эпоха Возрождения</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-center is-style-default\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://project/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1a7ee85e-7e66-507c-8513-a8f74050cc99-1024x640.jpg\",\"id\":35,\"dimRatio\":50,\"style\":{\"color\":{}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"></span><img class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-35\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://project/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1a7ee85e-7e66-507c-8513-a8f74050cc99-1024x640.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\"/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">Импрессионизм</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"wp-block-heading\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><a href=\"/impressionism\">Импрессионизм: революция в живописи</a></strong></strong></strong></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><em><em><em>Импрессионизм — это художественное направление, возникшее во Франции в конце XIX века и ставшее настоящей революцией в мире искусства. Художники-импрессионисты отказались от традиционных академических правил и начали экспериментировать с цветом, светом и формой, чтобы передать мгновенные впечатления от окружающего мира.</em></em></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:separator {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"100%\",\"className\":\"is-style-section-1\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-style-section-1\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"is-style-section-3\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"},\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"justifyContent\":\"left\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-style-section-3\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\"><!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://project/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0acaed0697fbd9882f38cbb6dcfbe131-4.jpg\",\"id\":76,\"dimRatio\":50,\"minHeight\":792,\"minHeightUnit\":\"px\",\"align\":\"right\",\"style\":{\"color\":{}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignright\" style=\"min-height:792px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"></span><img class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-76\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://project/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0acaed0697fbd9882f38cbb6dcfbe131-4.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\"/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">Современное искусство</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"},\"layout\":{\"columnSpan\":1,\"rowSpan\":1}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"space-between\",\"justifyContent\":\"stretch\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-default\"><strong><strong><strong><a href=\"/art\">Современное искусство: от авангарда до цифры</a></strong></strong></strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Современное искусство — это динамичный и многогранный мир, который постоянно меняется и бросает вызов традиционным представлениям о том, что такое искусство. Начиная с авангарда начала XX века и заканчивая цифровым искусством XXI века, современное искусство отражает сложность и разнообразие нашего мира.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":75,\"width\":\"651px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"aspectRatio\":\"1.7777777777777777\",\"scale\":\"cover\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"http://project/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/i-1.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-75\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1.7777777777777777;object-fit:cover;width:651px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|80\"},\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80)\"><!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-text-display\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"400\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center is-style-text-display\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">Есть вопросы? <br><a href=\"http://project/contacts/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"121\" rel=\"nofollow\">Не стесняйтесь обращаться.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /